description: Do you like cats? Want to know something more about them every day to tell your friends? With Cat Facts for Alexa, you now have a wealth of feline knowledge without needing to stop petting the kitty.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Cat Facts to tell me a fact
Alexa ask Cat Facts about a fact
name: Cat Facts
shortDescription: Cat Facts for Alexa. Because you need your hands to pet the cat.
